Removing outliers¶

In [8]:
from scipy import stats

# Calculate z-scores
numerical_columns = ['Age', 'RestingBP', 'Cholesterol', 'MaxHR', 'Oldpeak']
z_scores = stats.zscore(Data[numerical_columns])

# Finding a threshold
threshold = 3

# Finding and removeing outliers
outliers = Data[(abs(z_scores) > threshold).any(axis=1)]
df_no_outliers = Data[~Data.index.isin(outliers.index)]

print("Original dataset:", Data.shape)
print("Shape after removing outliers:", df_no_outliers.shape)

Original dataset: (918, 12)
Shape after removing outliers: (899, 12)

from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split
from sklearn.svm import SVC
from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score

A = df_scaled.drop('HeartDisease', axis=1)
B = df_no_outliers['HeartDisease']

# Training and testing sets
X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(A, B, test_size=0.2, random_state=42)

# Train the SVM model
svm_model = SVC()
svm_model.fit(X_train, y_train)

# Make predictions
svm_predictions = svm_model.predict(X_test)

# Calculate accuracy
svm_accuracy = accuracy_score(y_test, svm_predictions)
print("SVM Accuracy:", svm_accuracy)

SVM Accuracy: 0.8777777777777778
In [13]:
from sklearn.tree import DecisionTreeClassifier

# Train the Decision Tree model
dt_model = DecisionTreeClassifier(random_state=42)
dt_model.fit(X_train, y_train)

# Make predictions
dt_predictions = dt_model.predict(X_test)

# Calculate accuracy
dt_accuracy = accuracy_score(y_test, dt_predictions)
print("Decision Tree Accuracy:", dt_accuracy)

Decision Tree Accuracy: 0.7888888888888889
In [15]:
from sklearn.ensemble import BaggingClassifier

# SVM
bagging_svm_model = BaggingClassifier(base_estimator=SVC(), n_estimators=10, random_state=42)
bagging_svm_model.fit(X_train, y_train)
bagging_svm_predictions = bagging_svm_model.predict(X_test)
bagging_svm_accuracy = accuracy_score(y_test, bagging_svm_predictions)
print("SVM Accuracy:", bagging_svm_accuracy)

# Decision Tree
bagging_dt_model = BaggingClassifier(base_estimator=DecisionTreeClassifier(random_state=42), n_estimators=10, random_state=42)
bagging_dt_model.fit(X_train, y_train)
bagging_dt_predictions = bagging_dt_model.predict(X_test)
bagging_dt_accuracy = accuracy_score(y_test, bagging_dt_predictions)
print("Decision Tree Accuracy:", bagging_dt_accuracy)

SVM Accuracy: 0.8888888888888888
Decision Tree Accuracy: 0.8444444444444444
